lead_paragraph: The two-time defending Olympic champion Brazil women are chasing a golden three-peat on home soil this summer. The top-ranked Americans are seeking redemption in Rio and their first gold ever.

headline.print_headline: Brazilian Women Chase Golden Three-Peat on Home Soil
